These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, march, january
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Birthday   | february | april | march | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, soccer, cycling, swimming
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Sport   | soccer | parkour | swimming | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, mirinda, lemonade
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | tea | mirinda | milk | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, february, september, march
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Birthday   | february | july | march | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, whist, mah-jongg
1. the person playing canasta is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Game   | mah-jongg | whist | backgammon | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-6::.
