3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| Sport   | biathlon | volleyball | badminton | soccer |

