.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, accountant, librarian, doctor
1. the accountant is on the right of the librarian##1
2. the librarian is on the right of the doctor##1
3. the accountant is on the left or right of the freelancer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |   3   |   4    |
| Job   | doctor | librarian | accountant | freelancer |

