.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, purple, azure, lilac
1. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
4. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Color   | azure | purple | blood-red | lilac |

