.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, classical, indie, reggae
1. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
2. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
4. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | indie | classical | techno | reggae |

