.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, subway, snowmobile, boat
1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the boat##2
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Transport   | boat | subway | scooter | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-11::.
