2. the tower house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| House   | art-deco | gothic-revival | tower | farmhouse |

