.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-19::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, mystery, horror, thriller
1. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
4. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2     |    3    |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | western | mystery | thriller |

