.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, train, boat, motorbike
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
4. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Transport   | boat | train | ship | motorbike |

 